Concepts learned during this scrim:
1. how to add background images
2. how to add animated gifs - webp format for better transmissibility 
3. how to add fonts from google and from external source -(@font-face)
4. <span> tag - can be used for CTA texts and utility classes can be used
5. IDs vs classes- “id” is unique in a page and can only apply to at 
most one element, while “class” selector can apply to multiple elements
6. text - shadow - to improve readability
